text: I haven't played MMORPGs or any MMOs all that much, but it's obvious I have developed some kind of affection to ambient game music. I feel enthusiastic, even thrilled listening to this piece even though I've never played Ragnarock Online or anything the like. Despite player chats and other things breaking the illusion a little, the feeling of exploration and amazement is very hard to sweep away.

text:

Thanks again for opening my ears to something new!
